      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust spots and paint peeling, while the interior requires a deep clean and several repairs to the upholstery. This would be best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a source for parts.",
